item.description:
Come join us for a summer day of play at the July 2010 Meetup! PLEASE NOTE THE NEW LOCATION IN NATICK!

This month's activity will be announced soon, but we anticipate that it will involve learning a cool technique that we'll then practice in the ever-popular jam sessions. We expect to help people trade individually with each other, if they want, and we have some other surprises in store as well. Stay tuned.
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Diet Coke, a cell phone, a pile of art supplies and a big smile.
